# ─── Contact Form Delivery (Web3Forms) ──────────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com
# 2. Enter your email (e.g. info@freightrepublicllc.co)
# 3. Click "Create Access Key" — they email you a key instantly
# 4. Copy the key below, then rename this file from .env.example → .env
# 5. Restart `npm run dev` (or redeploy)
#
# Every form submission will now arrive in your inbox.
# Free tier: 250 submissions/month. No credit card. No ads in emails.
#
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=paste-your-access-key-here
